      "id": "features", 
      "name": "Features",
      "content": "## Core Features\n\n- **SBOM Ingestion**: Native support for CycloneDX, SPDX, and SWID Tag formats\n- **Vulnerability Intelligence**: Aggregates vulnerability data from multiple sources including NVD, GitHub Security Advisories, OSS Index, and VulnDB\n- **Policy Engine**: Define and enforce policies for security and license compliance\n- **REST API**: Extensive API for automation and CI/CD integration\n- **Portfolio Management**: Track components across all applications and projects\n- **Risk Assessment**: Calculate and track risk metrics across your software portfolio\n- **Component Intelligence**: Deep insights into component usage, versions, and vulnerabilities\n\n## Integration Capabilities\n\n- **Build Tools**: Maven, Gradle, NPM, Yarn, pip, and more\n- **CI/CD Platforms**: Jenkins, GitHub Actions, GitLab CI, Azure DevOps\n- **Container Scanning**: Docker, Kubernetes integration\n- **IDE Plugins**: Support for popular development environments\n\n## Reporting & Analytics\n\n- **Executive Dashboards**: High-level risk metrics and trends\n- **Detailed Reports**: Component inventories, vulnerability reports, compliance reports\n- **Metrics & KPIs**: Track security posture improvements over time\n- **Custom Reports**: Flexible reporting engine for specific organizational needs",
