or development and infrastructure\n- **Resources**: Provide development resources and expertise\n- **Use Cases**: Share success stories and case studies\n- **Partnerships**: Collaborate on integrations and improvements\n\n## Recognition\n\n### Industry Awards\n- **OWASP Flagship Project**: Recognized as a flagship OWASP project\n- **Industry Recognition**: Featured in security vendor reports and analyses\n- **Conference Presentations**: Regular presentations at major security conferences\n- **Academic Citations**: Referenced in academic research papers\n\n### Community Impact\n- **Download Statistics**: Hundreds of thousands of downloads\n- **Enterprise Adoption**: Used by major corporations worldwide\n- **Integration Ecosystem**: Extensive third-party tool integrations\n- **Educational Impact**: Used in cybersecurity training and education\n\nFor more information about supporting the OWASP Dependency-Track project, please contact the project leaders or visit our GitHub repository.",
